at quartz crystals.

00:21:43.980 --> 00:21:46.040
And he was studying various
quartz crystals.

00:21:46.040 --> 00:21:48.740
By that I mean, quartz crystals
of different sizes.

00:21:48.740 --> 00:21:50.900
And what he observed was, didn't
matter what the size of

00:21:50.900 --> 00:21:52.050
the crystal was.

00:21:52.050 --> 00:21:53.690
They always had the same
angles between

00:21:53.690 --> 00:21:55.240
corresponding faces.

00:21:55.240 --> 00:21:58.340
So if I give you a big crystal
